## ğŸ“± Landscape Centering for Phones

/* NEW CODE: Use a Media Query to target phone landscape orientation (devices up to 900px wide).
  This centers the entire gallery wrapper horizontally on a wide screen.
*/
@media only screen and (max-width: 900px) and (orientation: landscape) {
    
    /* âš ï¸ IMPORTANT: Replace '.gallery-container' with your actual wrapper class! */
    .gallery-container {
        /* Set a max width so the container doesn't stretch edge-to-edge */
        max-width: 700px; 
        /* Center the block element horizontally */
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        /* If your container uses flex/grid, you might also need this: */
        /* justify-content: center; */
    }
}

